japan march interim trade surplu fall japan 's customs-clear trade surplu fell to 1.89 billion dlr in the first 10 day of march from a 1.91 billion surplu a year earlier , the ministri of financ said . the march interim surplu compar with a 1.70 billion dlr surplu in the same februari period . fob export in the first 10 day of march rose 5.8 pct from a year earlier to 5.50 billion dlr and cif import rose 9.7 pct to 3.61 billion . the averag yen/dollar rate use for the statist wa 153.67 yen against 181.23 a year earlier .